      "span_text": "The obtained clean reads of all six samples were assembled using the Trinity program [CITATION_1] with the following parameters: k-mer = 25; minimum k-mer coverage = 2; maximum length expected between fragment pairs = 500; minimum overlap of reads with growing transcript PE = 75; maximum number of reads to anchor within a single graph = 200,000."
